<CTPLayout title={title}>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="title">
            <h1>Main</h1>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-h2">
        <h2>
            What's Crafting Table Plus ?
        </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="container-teks">
        <p>
            Crafting Table Plus is a mod for Minecraft java edition.
        </p>
        <p>
            This mod help you to create some items that cannot be crafted on the crafting table at Minecraft vanila.
        </p>
        <p>
            We created this mod to simplify gameplay in Minecraft, even though not everyone likes it, because this mod makes it easier for players to obtain rare items and superpowers, which may not be very challenging.   
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="container-h2">
        <h2>
            How is Crafting Table Plus created ?
        </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="container-teks">
        <p>
            Crafting Table Plus is made just by adding a new file of JSON type.
        </p>
        <p>
            This is certainly very easy, because it does not add new items and blocks, it only fills the JSON file with a specific script.
        </p>
    </div>  
    <div class="container-h2">
        <h2>
            How often does Crafting Table Plus update version ?
        </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="container-teks">
        <p>
            For version updates, every two weeks or once a month.
        </p>
        <p>
            Regarding the mod version update, it is actually not always in line with what was mentioned above, because if we have a new project, the update may be delayed.   
        </p>
    </div>  
    <div class="container-h2">
        <h2>
            Changelog
        </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="container-teks">
        <div class="version-new">
            <h3>Version: 1.17.1-1.0</h3>
        </div>
        <h4>
            Just a first version for Minecraft 1.17.1, no crafting items.
        </h4>
        <div class="changelog">
        
        </div>
    </div>
